Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:06.72,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N14
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.61,0:00:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近校内的风纪变得有些乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望担任学生辅导的樱井老师能更加严格地监管
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我正是为了改变自己才来担任学生辅导老师的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须好好地监管！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况  这突然出现的是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不行  我绝不能就这样退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  那什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边走边吃是不是稍微有失礼节…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没有吃早饭  所以肚子就突然嘶鸣起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就撤掉  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能理解就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  只要和他好好说还是懂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我传达下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊上发出这么大的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微考虑一下学校风纪行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  把那个带来学校的有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美里  要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原  午休的时候我有点话要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖给我待在教室里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  风纪是有点变乱了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬  立花美里她是没有恶意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么  你脖子前那轻飘飘的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  感觉有点可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在日常生活中度过的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上也许是连续发生的奇迹也说不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  就是那种东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个  那轻飘飘的到底是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗  哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎扯啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么女士  有机会的话我们课堂上见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:49.38,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be100\3c&HFFFFFF&}学\N生\N辅\N导
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换着看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  打扰一下  中之条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  有什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校留这种发型是不是稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是有点  只是有点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  要是没听清我再重复一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边的…两边的长不出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:29.37,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,350)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be100\3c&HFFFFFF&}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:29.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本小孩玩扮鬼游戏时念的咒语「ダルマさんが転んだ」  相当于一二三木头人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁它…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌倒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回去了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:40.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请再往前一千步
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:45.12,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N15
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是青梅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在家里做梅干试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅干…咸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅子对身体有益处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且加在饭团里  饭不容易坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀！  名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我还什么都没说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是买了一大堆点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把那些好好吃完  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了之后再来买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哟  今天已经和黑猫先生…叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  约好了买阪本先生的食物回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  请问您有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个  这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是雪人  今天上架的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您喜欢的话  请购买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看起来像是刨冰的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我…我只是看一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那不是雪人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个如果不买的话就给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我买
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  名乃明明就可以买自己想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士就要的就说「不行」！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不   因为这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃可以买自己想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士想买的东西也能买！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要  我想要  我就要嘛我就要！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我知道了  就只买一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢名乃了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就买了这种东西回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很可爱  而且冰冰凉的感觉也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  盛好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  再给我点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你们这帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我的饭在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:37.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}又是5-7-5的俳句格式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这顿饭是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又冰又凉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随口说说
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许乱出哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认输…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发条！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
