Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}恶搞E.T.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  考试结束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}传说事情失败时念此咒语可以消灾  相当于「我的天啊！」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无三宝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是假发
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
